Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:01:59.16,star,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:01.00,star,,0,0,0,,Stand up, Hyuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:06.64,star,,0,0,0,,Throw the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:07.72,star,,0,0,0,,Throw it!
